.TH "NAVIGATIONACTIVATION.FROM" "3JS" "December 8, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
NavigationActivation.from \- NavigationActivation: from property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]from\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]NavigationActivation\f[R] interface contains a
\f[CR]NavigationHistoryEntry\f[R] object representing the history entry
for the outgoing (\(lqfrom\(rq) document in the navigation.
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]NavigationHistoryEntry\f[R] object, or \f[CR]null\f[R] if the
outgoing document is:
.IP \(bu 2
Not same origin as the inbound document.
.IP \(bu 2
The initial \f[CR]about:blank\f[R] document.
.SH EXAMPLES
See the main \f[CR]NavigationActivation\f[R] page.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IP \(bu 2
Navigation API
.IP \(bu 2
View Transition API
